[SN]TITLE[SN]
Ex-Celtic Boys Club coach Jim Torbett appears in court

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Former Celtic Boys Club coach and founder Jim Torbett has appeared in court on a string of historical sex charges.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 69-year-old from Glasgow faces three charges of lewd, indecent and libidinous practices and behaviours, and three charges of indecent assault.
He appeared from custody in private at Glasgow Sheriff Court.
He made no plea and was released on bail by sheriff John McCormick.
